{"tid":1606891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若果你宜家心情仍未平伏，請馬上熄登、瞓覺","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:33.000Z","uid":273258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6aab1aa6e588ad34460e897e6088b826d20cdb75","tid":1606891,"uid":273258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"明白各位巴打絲打宜家嘅心情實係好難平伏<br />\n大戰前夕心入面一定好緊張、好stress<br />\n但係為左聽日請大家宜家即刻養精蓄銳<br />\n寧願聽照早啲起身預備行裝，收拾心情<br />\n就好似比賽一樣，將自己調教至最佳狀態<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n天佑我城<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c85eded727474a21f0090776ad0b684a02915d5f","tid":1606891,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔敢訓 好驚一訓聽日起來既來臨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827a6e8ea8e6eff6c0a613273933fe12e22df188","tid":1606891,"uid":273258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n十月一，賀佢老母"},{"pid":"ba67aa7b758e564e9df8b6c209dad9fb869a9fc0","tid":1606891,"uid":273258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c85eded727474a21f0090776ad0b684a02915d5f","tid":1606891,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔敢訓 好驚一訓聽日起來既來臨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"我明白<br />\n但有啲嘢係必須面對，不能逃避<br />\n盡量唔好俾自己諗嘢住，放鬆啲<br />\n聽照起身先繼續<br />\n加油"}]}